snippet.title: Rocket Rumble - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Rumble this summer on Steam!
https://www.rocketrumblegame.com

Rocket Rumble is a 2-4 player party game where a charming cast of animals in rocket suits smash and bash their way across the finish line. Play online or on the couch, customize your character and get ready to Rumble!

Coming to Steam Early Access Summer 2021!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1357430/Rocket_Rumble/

Join the community on Discord!
https://discord.gg/7JH9ZKT
